file_content.text: Inhale cautiously, chosen of Gray Secant! Geological yellow concave released poisonous gases on this world, posing biological hazards and interfering with data transmission.
At current rate of dissipation, transmission can resume after ten thousand local system revolutions. Until then, take my observational data with gray parallel!
Why do you respire here? Toxins inflict constant green concave! You should leave this world at once!
